elements.name: Verify user is able to add a product in to the cart

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters username and password
the user should see products page
the user clicks add to cart button in products:
the cart icon should indicate the count of products
the user clicks on cart icon
the user should see selected products in the cart

elements.name: Verify user is able to add multiple products to the cart

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters username and password
the user should see products page
the user clicks add to cart button in products:
the cart icon should indicate the count of products
the user clicks on cart icon
the user should see selected products in the cart

elements.name: Verify user is able to finish checkout products

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters username and password
the user should see products page
the user clicks add to cart button in products:
the user clicks on cart icon
the user should see selected products in the cart
the user clicks checkout button
the user should navigate to the checkout infromation page
the user enters checkout informations
the user clicks continue button
the user should navigate to the checkout overview page
the user should see the total amount of products selected
the user clicks finish button
a thank you message should be visble

elements.name: Verify user is able to login to the application

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters username and password
the user should see products page

elements.name: Verify user not able to login with invalid credentials

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters invalid username and password
the user should see error message
the user should not navigate to products page

elements.name: Verify user is able to logout from the application

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters username and password
the user should see products page
the user click logout button from the hamburger menu
the user should navigate to the login page

elements.name: Verify user is able to sort the products

steps.name: the user launches the browser with Swag Labs url
the user should see login page
the user enters username and password
the user should see products page
the user selects "Price (low to high)" from the product sort dropdown
the products should be sorted from lowest to highest price
